snippet.title: Zipp's Café - A World of Wilderness story / Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Love, betrayal, and coffee! This is Zipp's Café, a small and cozy café management sim, where you not only have to make delicious coffees and dinners but also solve some problems around your customers.

Grab it on Steam for the price of a coffee on November 15th, 2023!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1812180/

The game is a prelude to Chicken Police - Into the HIVE!, and part of the World of Wilderness.

You can find Chicken Police - Into the HIVE! below:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2362090/Chicken_Police_Into_the_HIVE/
